init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The man replies "I want you to be the next president."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: to you, "I know that you ran for 2 terms but someone new is in office.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are very skeptical of this man, but after some more conversation you agree to hear him out.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You begin to think about the 4 years you've had since your retirement.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You win and are elected once again as president of the United States.
